Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.13,JP,,0,0,118,,{\fn华文细黑\fs38\fscy106\fsp0\b0\blur0.2\bord0.6\shad1.2\4a80\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0F0F10&\4c&H50484A&}Please, list
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.48,JP,,0,0,0,,まずは探索の能力者を探すんだっけか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.82,JP,,0,0,0,,リーダーに聞いてみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:32.82,JP,,0,0,0,,間違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:43.00,JP,,0,0,0,,さて　どんな能力の持ち主やら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.33,JP,,0,0,0,,コイツか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.64,JP,,0,0,118,,{\fn华文细黑\fs38\fscy106\fsp0\b0\blur0.5\bord0.8\shad1.2\4a80\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0F0F10&\4c&H50484A&}If you move, you fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:02.98,JP,,0,0,118,,{\fn华文细黑\fs38\fscy106\fsp0\b0\blur0.5\bord0.8\shad1.2\4a80\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0F0F10&\4c&H50484A&}You are leader?
