Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.82,JP,,0,0,118,,{\fn华文细黑\fs38\fscy106\fsp0\b0\blur0.5\bord0.8\shad1.2\4a80\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0F0F10&\4c&H50484A&}Unusual ability player.
